E(VY) = E(V)E(Y)
   E(VY) = \frac{3}{4}\frac{1}{2} = \frac{3}{8}\text{.} 
   E(VY) = E(V)E(Y) = \frac{1}{2}\frac{3}{4} = \frac{3}{8} \text{.} 
